Package: safetyexploreR
Title: Safety Explorer charts from R
Version: 0.3.1
Description: safetyexploreR provides an R interface for Rho's safety explorer suite.  Underlying widgets are built using Webcharts and d3.js and have been converted to R functions using the htmlwidgets framwork. The six charts include: AE Explorer, AE Timelines, Safety Histogram, Safety Results Over Time, Safety Shift Plot, and Safety Outlier Explorer. This set of tools can be used individually or together, allowing a user to interact with clinical trials safety data in real time.
